latestIgtvVideos.title: Complete style guide to play around with your white shirt
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
_

No wardrobe is complete without a classic white shirt. One of the most useful and fun piece of clothing you can own. This fashion staple can be styled down for day, up for night and multiple other unique ways in between.

I’ve created eight looks using two white shirts. One is a classic and the other one has interesting sleeves to up the style game 🌸💗
